<hr>

<p class="light">
    Create tokens on the CLI:
    <code>php craft mcp/tokens/create --user=&lt;email&gt; --label="Claude" --ttl-days=90</code><br>
    Every tool call runs as the token's Craft user and is bounded by that user's permissions.
    Structural &amp; system operations additionally require an admin user and an explicit
    <code>confirm: true</code> argument.
</p>
